      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SHARP SPARK finished 6 lengths back in second over 2213m at this track (Dirt) last time out after a gutsy win the start prior. Has a decent record at this track. Likely to feature. 5. HEY TOBY turned in a nice effort to score two runs ago at this track. Couldn't follow that up last time out when sixth over 1609m at this track, beaten 7 lengths. Enjoys a drop in grade so he is a leading contender. 2. LAUGHING BOY lines up on the back of a 6 length fifth over 1609m at this track. Has a good record here at this journey with two wins from six starts. Among the main hopes. 4. CENTAVO showed good early dash and raced on the speed last start before fading to finish 6 lengths back in fourth over 2213m at this track (Dirt). Has ability and a bold showing is expected.\",\"runners\":[1,5,2,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
